messageBody:
FYI.

With the recent acquisition of TogetherSoft by Borland, the Coad
Letter is now part of the Borland Developer Network (bdn.borland.com).
Randy Miller is now part of the BDN and is editor-in-chief of the
Coad Letter. Randy also has a BDN "soapbox" on Agile development!

Dave
